    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you hit a creature with a weapon attack with a weapon with the heavy property, you can add 2 Flurry Die to the damage and force the creature and any other creature (no inlcuding you) within 5 feet of them to make a Strength saving throw.</p><p> On a failed save, a creature takes the damage of the flurry die and is knocked prone.</p><p> A frightened creature makes this save with disadvantage.</p><p></p>",
